{"tid":469913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔想自己再係咁睇ex既wtsapp last seen","createTime":"2017-11-15T19:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T16:01:50.000Z","uid":76951,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"97638eaccb603bc802368225d44d289203aaa559","tid":469913,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:24:17.000Z","msg":"近排唔知點解掛住返佢，有時諗起佢就手痕睇佢有冇on<br />\n都分咗幾個月，開頭覺得鬆一口氣，因為佢果排好冷淡，我問佢係咪想分手，佢間接咁認咗<br />\n終於知道結果，唔洗估估吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時想追返佢，不過諗到佢果陣同第二個男仔玩得咁開心，唔理我，嫌我煩<br />\n一個早唞都唔想同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分手前果個禮拜，我係幾咁唔開心，上上吓堂眼濕濕，同人食飯諗起佢咁對我，忍唔住流眼淚，唉<br />\n<br />\n我知道我應該要move on，同佢一齊咗唔係好耐，但係同佢既回憶，掛念既時候就係腦海中閃過<br />\n<br />\n返pt識有個女仔對我有好感，我對佢都有d好感，有幾次佢默默咁幫我做d野，我事後先知，果刻有d感動，有衝動想同佢一齊<br />\n但冷靜返之後，我第一個諗起既人係佢，我仲未放低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded31e3797bd41dae3d0d5f0fcc443c18464ee28","tid":469913,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:26:00.000Z","msg":"冇，放低左"},{"pid":"36c2a38f1a20b34314bd4cc840075955b4643dcc","tid":469913,"uid":29276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，lets bygone be bygone"},{"pid":"06c198afac9cd8b379e1b223e7e0ba59c0eddfe6","tid":469913,"uid":21782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T20:22:00.000Z","msg":"有咩好睇，睇完唔會返轉頭都唔會關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375489aaea1d811a7eb083f2268ad0cd9b61943a","tid":469913,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T21:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4eb6716bede9d6a9e82de3b4c665e519c73ec191","tid":469913,"uid":113598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T21:11:57.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住ex 努力忘記中 共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"